SET MoneyFormat='$#,##0.00;-$#,##0.00';
SET TimeFormat='h:mm:ss TT';

SET TimestampFormat='M/D/YYYY h:mm:ss[.fff] TT';

SQL SELECT

	"qConnectedUsers",
	"qFileTime",
	"qFileSize",
	"qDocId",
	"qLastReloadTime",
	"qTitle",
	"isCurrentApp",
	"__KEY_root",
	(SELECT 
		"hassectionaccess",
		"__FK_qMeta"
	FROM "qMeta" FK "__FK_qMeta"),
	(SELECT 
		"__FK_qThumbnail"
	FROM "qThumbnail" FK "__FK_qThumbnail"),
	(SELECT 
		"__KEY_qAppObjectList",
		"__FK_qAppObjectList",
		(SELECT 
			"__KEY_qItems",
			"__FK_qItems",
			(SELECT 
				"qId",
				"qType",
				"__FK_qInfo"
			FROM "qInfo" FK "__FK_qInfo"),
			(SELECT 
				"title",
				"description",
				"__KEY_qMeta",
				"__FK_qMeta_u0",
				(SELECT 
					"@Value",
					"__FK_privileges"
				FROM "privileges" FK "__FK_privileges" ArrayValueAlias "@Value")
			FROM "qMeta" PK "__KEY_qMeta" FK "__FK_qMeta_u0"),
			(SELECT 
				"rank",
				"columns",
				"rows",
				"title" AS "title_u0",
				"labelExpression",
				"description" AS "description_u0",
				"descriptionExpression",
				"__KEY_qData",
				"__FK_qData",
				(SELECT 
					"__KEY_thumbnail",
					"__FK_thumbnail",
					(SELECT 
						"__FK_qStaticContentUrl"
					FROM "qStaticContentUrl" FK "__FK_qStaticContentUrl")
				FROM "thumbnail" PK "__KEY_thumbnail" FK "__FK_thumbnail"),
				(SELECT 
					"name",
					"type",
					"col",
					"row",
					"colspan",
					"rowspan",
					"__KEY_cells",
					"__FK_cells",
					(SELECT 
						"y",
						"x",
						"width",
						"height",
						"__FK_bounds"
					FROM "bounds" FK "__FK_bounds")
				FROM "cells" PK "__KEY_cells" FK "__FK_cells")
			FROM "qData" PK "__KEY_qData" FK "__FK_qData")

	FROM "qAppObjectList" PK "__KEY_qAppObjectList" FK "__FK_qAppObjectList"),
	(SELECT 
		"qEmbeddedSnapshotRef" AS "qEmbeddedSnapshotRef_u1",
		"__KEY_sheets",
		"__FK_sheets",

			"qExtendsId",
			"qStateName",

			"columns" AS "columns_u0",
			"rows" AS "rows_u0",
			"gridResolution",
			"__KEY_qProperty",
			"__FK_qProperty",
			(SELECT 
				"qId" AS "qId_u0",
				"qType" AS "qType_u0",
				"__FK_qInfo_u0"
			FROM "qInfo" FK "__FK_qInfo_u0"),
			(SELECT 
				"title" AS "title_u1",
				"description" AS "description_u1",
				"__FK_qMetaDef"
			FROM "qMetaDef" FK "__FK_qMetaDef"),
			(SELECT 
				"__KEY_thumbnail_u0",
				"__FK_thumbnail_u0",
				(SELECT 
					"qUrl",
					"__FK_qStaticContentUrlDef"
				FROM "qStaticContentUrlDef" FK "__FK_qStaticContentUrlDef")

				"col" AS "col_u0",
				"row" AS "row_u0",
				"colspan" AS "colspan_u0",
				"rowspan" AS "rowspan_u0",
				"__KEY_cells_u0",
				"__FK_cells_u0",
				(SELECT 
					"y" AS "y_u0",
					"x" AS "x_u0",
					"width" AS "width_u0",
					"height" AS "height_u0",
					"__FK_bounds_u0"

			FROM "cells" PK "__KEY_cells_u0" FK "__FK_cells_u0"),
			(SELECT 
				"__KEY_qChildListDef",
				"__FK_qChildListDef",
				(SELECT 
					"title" AS "title_u2",
					"__FK_qData_u0"
				FROM "qData" FK "__FK_qData_u0")
			FROM "qChildListDef" PK "__KEY_qChildListDef" FK "__FK_qChildListDef"),

			"qEmbeddedSnapshotRef" AS "qEmbeddedSnapshotRef_u0",
			"__KEY_qChildren",
			"__FK_qChildren",
			(SELECT 
				"qExtendsId" AS "qExtendsId_u1",
				"qStateName" AS "qStateName_u2",
				"showTitles",
				"title" AS "title_u3",
				"subtitle",
				"footnote",
				"showDetails",
				"visualization",
				"version" AS "version_u0",
				"__KEY_qProperty_u0",
				"__FK_qProperty_u0",
				(SELECT 
					"qId" AS "qId_u1",
					"qType" AS "qType_u1",
					"__FK_qInfo_u1"
				FROM "qInfo" FK "__FK_qInfo_u1"),
				(SELECT 
					"__FK_qMetaDef_u0"
				FROM "qMetaDef" FK "__FK_qMetaDef_u0"),
				(SELECT 
					"fieldListO",
					"object",
					"cId",
					"fieldName",
					"state",
					"__FK_fieldList"
				FROM "fieldList" FK "__FK_fieldList"),
				(SELECT 
					"qStateName" AS "qStateName_u1",
					"qSuppressZero" AS "qSuppressZero_u0",
					"qSuppressMissing" AS "qSuppressMissing_u0",
					"qReductionMode" AS "qReductionMode_u0",
					"qMode" AS "qMode_u0",
					"qPseudoDimPos" AS "qPseudoDimPos_u0",
					"qNoOfLeftDims" AS "qNoOfLeftDims_u0",
					"qAlwaysFullyExpanded" AS "qAlwaysFullyExpanded_u0",
					"qMaxStackedCells" AS "qMaxStackedCells_u0",
					"qPopulateMissing" AS "qPopulateMissing_u0",
					"qShowTotalsAbove" AS "qShowTotalsAbove_u0",
					"qIndentMode" AS "qIndentMode_u0",
					"qSortbyYValue" AS "qSortbyYValue_u0",
					"__KEY_qHyperCubeDef",

					(SELECT 
						"@Value" AS "@Value_u0",
						"__FK_qDimensions"
					FROM "qDimensions" FK "__FK_qDimensions" ArrayValueAlias "@Value_u0"),
					(SELECT 
						"@Value" AS "@Value_u1",

					FROM "qMeasures" FK "__FK_qMeasures" ArrayValueAlias "@Value_u1"),
					(SELECT 
						"@Value" AS "@Value_u2",
						"__FK_qInterColumnSortOrder"

						"qWidth",
						"qHeight",

						"qv",

					FROM "qCalcCond" FK "__FK_qCalcCond"),
					(SELECT 
						"qv" AS "qv_u0",
						"__FK_qTitle"
					FROM "qTitle" FK "__FK_qTitle"),
					(SELECT 
						"__KEY_qCalcCondition",
						"__FK_qCalcCondition",
						(SELECT 
							"qv" AS "qv_u1",

					(SELECT 
						"@Value" AS "@Value_u3",
						"__FK_qColumnOrder"

					(SELECT 
						"@Value" AS "@Value_u4",

							"qMode",
							"qPseudoDimPos",
							"qNoOfLeftDims",
							"qAlwaysFullyExpanded",
							"qMaxStackedCells",
							"qPopulateMissing",
							"qShowTotalsAbove",
							"qIndentMode",
							"qSortbyYValue",
							"__KEY_qHyperCubeDef_u0",

							(SELECT

								"__FK_qDimensions_u0"
							FROM "qDimensions" FK "__FK_qDimensions_u0" ArrayValueAlias "@Value_u5"),
							(SELECT 
								"@Value" AS "@Value_u6",
								"__FK_qMeasures_u0"
							FROM "qMeasures" FK "__FK_qMeasures_u0" ArrayValueAlias "@Value_u6"),
							(SELECT 
								"@Value" AS "@Value_u7",
								"__FK_qInterColumnSortOrder_u0"

							(SELECT 
								"@Value" AS "@Value_u8",
								"__FK_qInitialDataFetch_u0"
							FROM "qInitialDataFetch" FK "__FK_qInitialDataFetch_u0" ArrayValueAlias "@Value_u8"),
							(SELECT 
								"qv" AS "qv_u3",
								"__FK_qCalcCond_u0"
							FROM "qCalcCond" FK "__FK_qCalcCond_u0"),
							(SELECT 
								"qv" AS "qv_u4",
								"__FK_qTitle_u0"
							FROM "qTitle" FK "__FK_qTitle_u0"),
							(SELECT 
								"__KEY_qCalcCondition_u0",
								"__FK_qCalcCondition_u0",
								(SELECT 
									"qv" AS "qv_u5",
									"__FK_qCond_u0"
								FROM "qCond" FK "__FK_qCond_u0"),
								(SELECT 
									"qv" AS "qv_u6",
									"__FK_qMsg_u0"
								FROM "qMsg" FK "__FK_qMsg_u0")
							FROM "qCalcCondition" PK "__KEY_qCalcCondition_u0" FK "__FK_qCalcCondition_u0"),
							(SELECT 
								"@Value" AS "@Value_u9",
								"__FK_qColumnOrder_u0"
							FROM "qColumnOrder" FK "__FK_qColumnOrder_u0" ArrayValueAlias "@Value_u9"),
							(SELECT 
								"@Value" AS "@Value_u10",
								"__FK_qExpansionState_u0"
							FROM "qExpansionState" FK "__FK_qExpansionState_u0" ArrayValueAlias "@Value_u10")
						FROM "qHyperCubeDef" PK "__KEY_qHyperCubeDef_u0" FK "__FK_qHyperCubeDef_u0")
					FROM "qLayoutExclude" PK "__KEY_qLayoutExclude" FK "__FK_qLayoutExclude")
				FROM "qHyperCubeDef" PK "__KEY_qHyperCubeDef" FK "__FK_qHyperCubeDef"),

					"author",

					(SELECT

			FROM "qProperty" PK "__KEY_qProperty_u0" FK "__FK_qProperty_u0"),
			(SELECT 
				"qEmbeddedSnapshotRef",
				"__KEY_qChildren_u0",
				"__FK_qChildren_u0",
				(SELECT 
					"qExtendsId" AS "qExtendsId_u2",
					"qStateName" AS "qStateName_u4",
					"title" AS "title_u4",
					"visualization" AS "visualization_u0",
					"__KEY_qProperty_u1",
					"__FK_qProperty_u1",
					(SELECT 
						"qId" AS "qId_u2",
						"qType" AS "qType_u2",
						"__FK_qInfo_u2"
					FROM "qInfo" FK "__FK_qInfo_u2"),
					(SELECT 
						"__FK_qMetaDef_u1"
					FROM "qMetaDef" FK "__FK_qMetaDef_u1"),
					(SELECT 
						"qStateName" AS "qStateName_u3",
						"qLibraryId",
						"qAutoSortByState",
						"qFrequencyMode",
						"qShowAlternatives",
						"__KEY_qListObjectDef",
						"__FK_qListObjectDef",
						(SELECT

								"qSortByExpression",
								"qSortByGreyness",
								"__KEY_qSortCriterias",
								"__FK_qSortCriterias",
								(SELECT

								"@Value" AS "@Value_u14",
								"__FK_qNumberPresentations"
							FROM "qNumberPresentations" FK "__FK_qNumberPresentations" ArrayValueAlias "@Value_u14")

						(SELECT

				FROM "qProperty" PK "__KEY_qProperty_u1" FK "__FK_qProperty_u1"),
				(SELECT

	FROM "sheets" PK "__KEY_sheets" FK "__FK_sheets")
FROM JSON (wrap on) "root" PK "__KEY_root";
